  m_text: '1. Follow the 20-20-20 rule: Rest the eyes during prolonged screen use.

    2.
    Maintain proper reading distance: Keep books and screens at a comfortable distance
    from the eyes.

    3. Use adequate lighting: Prevent unnecessary eye strain
    while reading or working.

    4. Spend time outdoors: Natural light may help
    reduce the progression of myopia.

    5. Limit excessive screen time: Reduce
    prolonged exposure to digital devices.

    6. Eat a healthy diet: Consume foods
    rich in vitamins and nutrients that support eye health.

    7. Schedule regular
    eye checkups: Early detection and proper management help maintain good vision.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
