  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "1. Blink frequently while using screens to prevent dryness and eye fatigue.\n2.
    Follow the 20-20-20 rule to reduce digital eye strain.\n3. Maintain a proper
    reading distance of about 35\u201340 cm from books and screens.\n4. Use adequate
    lighting while reading or working to avoid unnecessary strain on the eyes.\n5.
    Eat a nutritious diet rich in vitamins and minerals that support eye health.\n6.
    Drink plenty of water to keep your eyes hydrated.\n7. Get sufficient sleep every
    day to allow your eyes to rest and recover.\n8. Wear sunglasses when outdoors
    to protect your eyes from harmful UV rays.\n9. Avoid rubbing your eyes, as it
    can cause irritation and increase the risk of infection.\n10. Schedule regular
    eye examinations to detect and address vision problems early.\n\nProper eye care
    helps maintain clear vision, reduces eye strain, and supports overall eye health."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
