  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "1. Clear vision for both near and distant objects.\n2. Light focuses exactly
    on the retina.\n3. No need for corrective lenses.\n4. Good depth perception.\n5.
    Normal color perception.\n6. Wide field of view.\n\n\nHOW IT WORKS:\n\r\n\u2022
    Cornea refracts incoming light\r\n\u2022 Lens fine-tunes focus (accommodation)\r\n\u2022
    Light lands precisely on the retina\r\n\u2022 Optic nerve sends signals to brain\r\n"
